      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle transcends the standard pre-owned category, offering a flawless exterior profile paired with a pristine, meticulously preserved interior. Every mechanical component has been verified to meet our most rigorous standards, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising automotive investment, this motorcar represents the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
